
WEAPONTYPES:

   1.) Slashing Weapons:

       Slashing weapons are mostly swords and axes. The damage
       a slashing weapon does depends on your strength and 
       dexterity and the quality of the weapon.

   2.) Piercing Weapons:

       Piercing weapons are mostly daggers and knives. The damage
       a piercing weapon does depends on your dexterity and the
       quality of the weapon.

   3.) Bludgeon Weapons:

       Bludgeon weapons are mostly clubs and hammers. The damage
       a bludgeon weapon does depends on your strength and the
       quality of the weapon.

